00:07:35.270 --> 00:07:37.400
How serious are Feng Lang's injuries?

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:38.680
The sword wound is deep,

00:07:38.680 --> 00:07:40.000
but it missed the vital organs,

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.190
